"""
CUI Reduction System

Reduces extracted CUIs through filtering, hierarchy pruning,
embedding-based redundancy removal, and structural confidence scoring.
Groups results into topics. Context-agnostic — no text embedding.

Output per CUI: confidence score, retention map, source chunks, topic.

pip install google-cloud-bigquery networkx numpy requests scann
"""

